{"tid":2493373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大碼Model｜重男友一倍家人難祝福 286磅大碼模特兒愛上拍時裝泳照：做自己最幸福","createTime":"2021-04-17T23:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T12:28:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":89,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c4714ace445653ecc0c820637dda4c179a9e27","tid":2493373,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T23:52:15.000Z","msg":"Leslie Chan在社交平台上載了她為外國泳衣品牌拍攝的模特兒硬照，相中她所穿的，是一件黑色伴有花朵的連身泳衣。她的臉、手臂、胸口及腹部，都被陽光所包圍。這是她最滿意的模特兒硬照，但在帖文的留言中，卻出現了一個「嘔嘔emoji」。<br />\n<br />\n現年23歲的Leslie拿着手機，飛快地打了一句英文「I know you&rsquo;re having a bad day, good luck to you」，然後她得到的回應，就是那位用戶對她的封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n這可不是一宗個別例子，就算離開網絡世界，Leslie走在街上，或走進親戚甚至男友家，她都會受到不少訝異目光及注視。但奈何，她是一位時常昂首站在鎂光燈底下的模特兒&mdash;&mdash;一位加大碼模特兒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210418/CWKLYZ7X5RDTZFKF32FRTNEXP4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210418%2FCWKLYZ7X5RDTZFKF32FRTNEXP4%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=1575dec7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210418%2FCWKLYZ7X5RDTZFKF32FRTNEXP4%2F&h=562c0b21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210418/CWKLYZ7X5RDTZFKF32FRTNEXP4/</a>"},{"pid":"cb8eee9d1e0335da079bb785f1bbd0b8ddd7ea1f","tid":2493373,"uid":34410,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T23:54:09.000Z","msg":"要幾多枝美極先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8fda0fd705e7db78002a1cbd85412d2505a94c","tid":2493373,"uid":102187,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T23:55:08.000Z","msg":"仲要扮大方回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074005c43804806fd19bb1571342cefa3476101b","tid":2493373,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T23:55:30.000